<h2 class="bold font-l">Halo 5 brute plasma rifle</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The Brute Plasma Rifle is used to destroy opponents' shields so that their health is vulnerable to kinetic weaponry. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="vsxglb" data-video-descrip="Plasma weapons, made with vague space science, as opposed to lasers." data-video-title="Plasma Rifle" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/vsxglb_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/57bbb455_3f24_4ba6_8b0c_757387383d7a.jpeg" data-video-trope="Main/PlasmaCannon" data-video-tropename="Plasma Cannon" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WebAnimation/TerribleWritingAdvice" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/57bbb455_3f24_4ba6_8b0c_757387383d7a.jpeg">
